{"tid":1610330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以應承我","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T01:23:42.000Z","uid":64003,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c25de1ffdd8696fddf532bb0acb6c193dda3b9df","tid":1610330,"uid":64003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"- 拆舖還拆舖 但唔好偷人地啲錢同貨<br />\n你打爛佢啲嘢、dum曬佢啲貨我唔理 但偷嘢會令人以為抗爭係為咗一己私慾<br />\n<br />\n- 揸緊春袋<br />\n廣告損失大過資訊板 電子貴過實體 收費位有價值過顯示位 爐重要過枱櫈⋯⋯<br />\n有價值嘅嘢不妨做先 同埋做得撤底啲 咁先可以喺短時間之內 得到最多回報<br />\n<br />\n- 做個真漢子<br />\n想講929去入境事務處條橋 班勇武子彈都唔怕 就咁拎住把遮衝過去班綠衫到<br />\n哩個無懼嘅精神係有需要承傳落去<br />\n<br />\n- 情況許可下 一定要救人<br />\n岳義士救人 但無人救岳義士 點解？<br />\n<br />\n- 一係做嘢 一係撤退 唔好企係到等被人拉<br />\n白衫佬斬人 你地成班企喺到 係唔會令到佢地驚㗎<br />\n<br />\n-保持理性 克制 諗下咁做嘅目的係咩<br />\n留有用之驅 做有用之事"},{"pid":"8dba76c1a421deef8396568f4fcbb2343c2e49c1","tid":1610330,"uid":64003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"400b0d9025f7bfdb7ca497f7bd92eecae792370f","tid":1610330,"uid":274801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7462cf16d0105fb4f063f48223fc3f33cc9d1b22","tid":1610330,"uid":32883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:26:13.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7106ccd0e4e367d2ae60ead1dc28ad254eb8ad67","tid":1610330,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:39:02.000Z","msg":"721 831<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1610306/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1610306/page/1</a><br />\nSSP賽後檢討 一齊討論下"},{"pid":"ea8716607e3cb56c2d996cec6887958bcd38154c","tid":1610330,"uid":310675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite